=== 市場 ===
2009年2月，電影公司宣布該專營權的名稱為《吸血新世紀》，各輯書名之間以冒號分隔開，而電影出現的標題只簡稱為「新月」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2009/02/19/twilight-exclusive-new-moon-art-and-official-title-revealed/|title=News - Entertainment, Music, Movies, Celebrity|website=MTV News|accessdate=2018-04-29|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090221043928/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2009/02/19/twilight-exclusive-new-moon-art-and-official-title-revealed/|archivedate=2009-02-21}}</ref>。首張宣傳海報於2009年5月19日發行<ref>{{cite web |author=Adam Rosenberg |title=Attention 'Twilight'-ers: The New 'New Moon' Poster Has Arrived! |url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2009/05/19/attention-twilight-ers-the-new-new-moon-poster-has-arrived/ |work=[[MTV|MTV]] |publisher=[[MTV_Networks|MTV Networks]] |date=2009-05-19 |accessdate=2009-05-19 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090521103109/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2009/05/19/attention-twilight-ers-the-new-new-moon-poster-has-arrived/ |archivedate=2009-05-21 }}</ref>。同年5月31日，羅拔·柏迪臣、姬絲汀·史超域以及泰勒·洛納於[[MTV影視大獎|MTV影視大獎]]揭曉了該電影的首支預告片<ref>{{cite web |author=Eric Ditzian |title='New Moon' Trailer To Premiere On MTV Movie Awards |url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1612292/20090528/story.jhtml |work=[[MTV|MTV]] |publisher=[[MTV_Networks|MTV Networks]] |date=2009-05-28 |accessdate=2009-05-29 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090529194818/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1612292/20090528/story.jhtml |archivedate=2009-05-29 }}</ref>。發行預告片後，電影中兩個場景於2009年的《[[圣地亚哥国际漫画展|聖地亞哥國際漫畫展]]》上展出<ref>{{cite web |author=Jen Yamato |title=Two ''New Moon'' Scenes Unveiled at Comic-Con: Full Description! |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/comic_con_2009/news/1833595/two_new_moon_scenes_unveiled_at_comic_con_full_description |website=Rotten Tomatoes |date=2009-07-23 |accessdate=2010-10-13 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100916070048/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/comic_con_2009/news/1833595/two_new_moon_scenes_unveiled_at_comic_con_full_description |archivedate=2010-09-16 }}</ref>。2009年8月12日，一段14秒的第二支預告片預覽於線上發布，而全長預告片在電影《{{le|搖滾未來|Bandslam}}》於劇院上映前曾播放過<ref>{{cite web |author=Adam Rosenberg |title='District 9' And A 'New Moon' Trailer Highlight This Week's Box Office Poll |url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2009/08/10/district-9-and-a-new-moon-trailer-highlight-this-weeks-box-office-poll/#more-19500 |publisher=MTV Networks |work=MTV |date=2009-08-10 |accessdate=2009-08-11 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090814121107/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2009/08/10/district-9-and-a-new-moon-trailer-highlight-this-weeks-box-office-poll#more-19500 |archivedate=2009-08-14 }}</ref>。電影的第三支預告片於2009年9月13日的《[[2009年MTV音樂錄影帶大獎|2009年MTV音樂錄影帶大獎]]》上放映<ref>{{cite web |author=Terri Schwartz |title='New Moon': Abbreviated Version Of The VMA Trailer Shown Before 'Sorority Row' & We've Seen It! |url=http://hollywoodcrush.mtv.com/2009/09/11/new-moon-abbreviated-version-of-the-vma-trailer-shown-before-sorority-row-weve-seen-it/ |publisher=MTV Networks |work=MTV |date=2009-09-11 |accessdate=2009-09-11 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090914115815/http://hollywoodcrush.mtv.com/2009/09/11/new-moon-abbreviated-version-of-the-vma-trailer-shown-before-sorority-row-weve-seen-it |archivedate=2009-09-14 }}</ref>。[[派拉蒙電視網|Spike TV]]在2009年10月27日的《尖叫獎2009》中也播出新預告片<ref>{{cite web |author=Amy Wilkinson |title=World Premiere 'New Moon' Footage To Air At Spike's Scream Awards |url=http://hollywoodcrush.mtv.com/2009/10/28/spike-tvs-scream-2009-best-moments-include-taylor-lautner-alexander-skarsgard-more/ |publisher=MTV |date=2009-10-14 |accessdate=2010-10-13 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100507191357/http://hollywoodcrush.mtv.com/2009/10/28/spike-tvs-scream-2009-best-moments-include-taylor-lautner-alexander-skarsgard-more/ |archivedate=2010-05-07 }}</ref>。

