== 反應 ==
=== 票房 ===
《新月》創下了美國（美國和加拿大）國內票房史上最高的午夜票房紀錄，在3,514間電影院中，估計票房收益為$2,630萬美元<ref name="Finke">{{cite web |author=Nikki Finke |title='New Moon' Shreds Movie Records! $258.8M Worldwide 5-Day Total! $140.7M Domestic Weekend Is All-Time 3rd Biggest; 'Blind Side' Big, Too |url=http://www.deadline.com/2009/11/phenomenal-breaking-records-new-moon-doing-dark-knight-midnight-numbers/#more-18958 |publisher=Mail.com Media Corporation |work=Deadline Hollywood |date=2009-11-21 |accessdate=2010-10-13 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110511114235/http://www.deadline.com/2009/11/phenomenal-breaking-records-new-moon-doing-dark-knight-midnight-numbers/#more-18958 |archivedate=2011-05-11 }}</ref>。打破了先前由《[[哈利波特：混血王子的背叛_(電影)|哈利波特：混血王子的背叛]]》所創下$2,220萬美元的午夜首映國內票房記錄<ref name="Finke"/>。在2010年，其續集《[[暮光之城3：蝕|吸血新世紀3：月蝕傳奇]]》打破了《新月》於4,000多個影院上映，收益達$3,000萬美元的記錄<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.the-numbers.com/interactive/newsStory.php?newsID=5247 |title=Eclipse Starts with $30 Million Overnight Record |publisher=The Numbers |date=2010-06-30 |accessdate=2010-10-13 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100704050719/http://www.the-numbers.com/interactive/newsStory.php?newsID=5247 |archivedate=2010-07-04 }}</ref>，然而它被《[[哈利·波特与死亡圣器（下）|哈利波特：死神的聖物Ⅱ]]》超越，後者在2011年的收益為$4,350萬美元<ref>[http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-report-final-harry-211757 Box Office Report: Final 'Harry Potter' Grosses a Record-Breaking $43.5 Million in Midnight Runs] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718084119/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-report-final-harry-211757 |date=2011-07-18 }}. ''[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]''. 2011年7月15日檢索</ref>。電影於國內首映當日就獲得$7,270萬美元的票房，成為美國國內史上最大的單日票房，超越了《[[黑暗騎士|蝙蝠俠—黑夜之神]]》的$6,720萬美元收入的記錄<ref name="Variety"/>。這個首映為另一項紀錄作出了重要貢獻—這就是美國國內票房前十名的電影首次單日總收入超過$1億美元的記錄<ref name="BoxOffice">{{cite web |author=Brandon Gray |title='New Moon' Shatters Opening Day Record |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2626&p=.htm |publisher=IMDb.com, Inc. |work=Box Office Mojo |date=2009-11-21 |accessdate=2009-11-21 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091124101014/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2626&p=.htm |archivedate=2009-11-24 }}</ref>。該記錄後來在2011年被《哈利波特：死神的聖物Ⅱ》賺得$9,110萬美元打破<ref name="Opening Day Record" />。

《新月》的開畫周末成為了美國國內史上最高開畫周末的第九位，其票房為$142,839,137美元<ref>{{cite web |title=Biggest Opening Weekends at the Box Office |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/ |publisher=IMDb.com, Inc. |work=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2009-11-23 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070309023608/http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/ |archivedate=2007-03-09 }}</ref>，並且也是全球最高開畫周末的第十位，總收入達2.749億美元<ref>{{cite web |title=All Time Worldwide Opening Records at the Box Office |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/worldwideopenings.htm |publisher=IMDb.com, Inc. |work=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2009-11-23 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110623165250/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/worldwideopenings.htm |archivedate=2011-06-23 }}</ref>。這部電影在發行時創下了11月最高的周末首映紀錄，打破了《[[哈利波特：火盃的考驗_(電影)|哈利波特：火盃的考驗]]》的記錄（$1.027億美元）<ref>{{cite news |author=Joal Ryan |title=New Moon Makes a Lot of Money (But Not Quite Batman Money) |url=http://www.eonline.com/news/154969/new-moon-makes-a-lot-of-money-but-not-quite-batman-money |publisher=E! Online |date=2009-11-23 |accessdate=2013-11-24 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150430041542/http://www.eonline.com/news/154969/new-moon-makes-a-lot-of-money-but-not-quite-batman-money |archivedate=2015-04-30 }}</ref>，直至被《[[飢餓遊戲：星火燎原_(電影)|飢餓遊戲2：星火燎原]]》的1.581億美元所超越<ref>{{cite news|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3756&p=.htm|title=Weekend Report: 'Catching Fire' Burns Bright, Sets November Record|date=2013-11-24|publisher=boxofficemojo.com|accessdate=2013-11-26|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6LOZ6Kr3F?url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3756&p=.htm|archivedate=2013-11-25}}</ref>。這部電影的預算估計不足$5,000萬美元，是全球上映成本超過2億美元的電影中最便宜的一部<ref>{{cite news |author=Ben Fritz |title='New Moon' sends box office soaring |url=http://www.latimes.com/business/la-fi-ct-boxoffice23-2009nov23,0,7443576.story |newspaper=Los Angeles Times |date=2009-11-23 |accessdate=2009-11-23 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091125084345/http://www.latimes.com/business/la-fi-ct-boxoffice23-2009nov23,0,7443576.story |archivedate=2009-11-25 }}</ref>。在感恩節的周末，這部電影票房收入為4,250萬美元，當中包括周三和周四約$6,600萬美元的票房。自上星期的開畫周末以來，電影已賺得$2.307億美元，比[[暮光之城：無懼的愛|上集]]的整個票房收入高出22％。在國際上，這部電影在整個周末的收入約$8,500萬美元，全球總收入在10天內達到$4.737億美元<ref name="ThanksgivingBoxOffice">{{cite web |author=Edward Douglas |title=New Moon & Blind Side Dominate Turkey Weekend |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=61207 |publisher=ComingSoon.net |date=2009-11-29 |accessdate=2009-11-29 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091202004148/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=61207 |archivedate=2009-12-02 }}</ref>。在其第三個周末，《新月》在美國國內市場獲得$1,570萬美元的票房<ref name="test">{{cite web |url=http://www.the-numbers.com/interactive/newsStory.php?newsID=4657 |title=The Numbers News – Weekend Estimates: Blind Side Scores in 3rd |publisher=The-numbers.com |date=2009-12-06 |accessdate=2010-06-15 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091212224023/http://www.the-numbers.com/interactive/newsStory.php?newsID=4657 |archivedate=2009-12-12 }}</ref>，以及國際上的另外賺得的$4,070萬美元，全球總收入為$5.701億美元。在第四個周末，該電影以$1,000萬美元的票房收益跌至第四位，其國內票房總額為$296,623,634美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/ |title=Weekend Box Office Results for June 11–13, 2010 |website=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2010-06-15 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100614183248/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/ |archivedate=2010-06-14 }}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
《新月》受到評論家的普遍負面的評價。評論網站《[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]》報導指，從226位評論家中，給予了積極評價的只有28％，其平均得分為4.69／10。該網站的普遍共識是：「吸血新世紀的第二輯可能會讓忠心粉絲滿意，但外人可能會因為它節奏緩慢、無情語氣和篇幅過於冗長而關掉它<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/twilight_saga_new_moon/|title = The Twilight Sage: New Moon (2009)|work = [[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher = [[IGN_Entertainment|IGN Entertainment]]|accessdate=2009-10-29|dead-url = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100106010635/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/twilight_saga_new_moon/|archivedate = 2010-01-06}}</ref>。」在《[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]》，它從電影評論家的100條評論中計算了[[加權平均數|平均得分]]，這部電影基於32條評論中，得分為44分<ref name="CNET Networks"/>。在《[[影院評分|影院評分]]》中的觀眾調查裡，觀眾給予該電影「A-」的級別<ref name="cinemsacore-bd1">{{Cite web |url=http://ew.com/article/2011/11/19/breaking-dawn-cinemascore-doesnt-sparkle/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2019-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190524021749/https://ew.com//article/2011/11/19/breaking-dawn-cinemascore-doesnt-sparkle/ |archive-date=2019-05-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《{{le|克利夫蘭現場|Cleveland Scene}}》的羅伯特·伊格尼齊奧（Robert Ignizio）形容電影是一個「娛樂幻想」，並指出「它比《吸血新世紀》更具視覺效果，並且在動作場景上做得更好，同時仍將注意力集中於三角戀的中心上<ref>{{cite news |author=Robert Ignizio |title=Twilight sequel is better than its predecessor |url=http://www.clevescene.com/reel-cleveland/archives/2009/11/19/twilight-sequel-is-better-than-its-predecessor |newspaper=Cleveland Scene |date=2009-11-19 |accessdate=2009-11-19 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091122202418/http://www.clevescene.com/reel-cleveland/archives/2009/11/19/twilight-sequel-is-better-than-its-predecessor |archivedate=2009-11-22 }}</ref>。」《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》的米高·奧沙利文（Michael O'Sullivan）給從4顆星中給電影2.5顆，他讚賞姬絲汀·史超域於電影中的表現並寫道：「儘管劇情有時足以誘發糖尿病，但這個性感和恐怖的嬉戲中卻得到足夠的狼哨聲以取悅其他人<ref>{{cite news |author=Michael O'Sullivan |title=The Twilight Saga: New Moon |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/gog/movies/the-twilight-saga-new-moon,1158191/critic-review.html |newspaper=The Washington Post |date=2009-11-20 |accessdate=2009-11-21 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121109153311/http://www.washingtonpost.com/gog/movies/the-twilight-saga-new-moon,1158191/critic-review.html |archivedate=2012-11-09 }}</ref>。」《[[西雅圖郵訊報|西雅圖郵訊報]]》給電影評為B級，並寫道：「電影看起來很棒，對話很有效，有很多擺好位置的笑話，演戲也到位<ref>{{cite news |author=Laremy Legel |title=Review: 'New Moon' a definite improvement |url=http://www.seattlepi.com/movies/412456_film30970631.html |publisher=Hearst Seattle Media |work=Seattle Post-Intelligencer |date=2009-11-19 |accessdate=2009-11-21 |archive-date=2018-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180429013919/https://www.seattlepi.com/ae/movies/article/Review-New-Moon-a-definite-improvement-887579.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。」

《{{le|紐約超時|Time Out Group}}》在5顆星中給了這部電影4顆，稱其為「對於那些年紀足夠大的人來說，卻又看到還年輕到可以在不死的夢想船上尖叫，這是可以接受的逃避現實<ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://newyork.timeout.com/articles/film/80595/the-twilight-saga-new-moon-film-review |title=The Twilight Saga: New Moon |last=Smith |first=Anna |magazine=Time Out |accessdate=2009-11-17 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091120011725/http://newyork.timeout.com/articles/film/80595/the-twilight-saga-new-moon-film-review |archivedate=2009-11-20 }}</ref>。」《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》的佐敦·明澤（Jordan Mintzer）指，「史超域是電影的心臟與靈魂」，他補充指她「賦予了對話的力量和深度……這聽起來像是一個不那麼吸引人的女演員嘴裡像典型的小雞般的泡沫，她使貝拉的心理創傷看起來像是真實的<ref>{{cite news |author=Jordan Mintzer |title=New Moon Review |url=http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117941623.html?categoryid=31&cs=1 |publisher=Reed Elsevier Inc. |work=Variety |date=2009-11-18 |accessdate=2009-11-19 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091121025851/http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117941623.html?categoryid=31&cs=1 |archivedate=2009-11-21 }}</ref>。」

英國電影評論家{{le|馬克·克莫德|Mark Kermode}}對電影進行了正面評價，說：「經過最初的20分鐘向下傾斜後，當我想到『實際上這將是兩個小時的拖把，我認為它找到了自己的腳。』」他還為泰勒·洛納的角色辯解，「看到迷迷的感覺，年輕人們穿過森林脫下上衣有點傻笑誘導。但這個很好，他們知道目標觀眾是甚麼<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F3Ckw7zLQ8o|title=The Twilight Saga: New Moon reviewed by Mark Kermode|publisher=YouTube|accessdate=2014-11-26|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150525224556/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F3Ckw7zLQ8o|archivedate=2015-05-25}}</ref>。」

《[[旧金山纪事报|三藩市紀事報]]》的米克·拉薩爾（Mick Lasalle）作出了更為複雜的評論，指：「預期這部電影能滿足其粉絲。其他人就準備來一場古怪的肥皂劇／選美大賽，由主角進入框架以準確宣布他們的想法的一系列靜態場景組成<ref>{{cite news |author=Mick LaSalle |title=Review: 'Twilight Saga: New Moon' |url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2009/11/19/DD0O1AN7L9.DTL |work=San Francisco Chronicle |publisher=Hearst Communications Inc. |date=2009-11-19 |accessdate=2009-11-19 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091122072544/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2009%2F11%2F19%2FDD0O1AN7L9.DTL |archivedate=2009-11-22 }}</ref>。」《[[數碼間諜|數碼間諜]]》從5顆星給這部電影2顆星，讚揚姬絲汀·史超域「將電影扛在肩上，再一次給了一個本來會自我放縱的角色帶來了很多靈魂」，但批評它缺乏行動，最終稱其為「流失的經歷」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/moviereviews/a186951/the-twilight-saga-new-moon.html |title=The Twilight Saga: New Moon |last=Papamichael |first=Stella |date=2009-11-17 |publisher=Digital Spy Limited |work=digitalspy.co.uk |accessdate=2009-11-17 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091120062450/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/moviereviews/a186951/the-twilight-saga-new-moon.html |archivedate=2009-11-20 }}</ref>。[[罗杰·伊伯特|羅渣·伊拔]]在4顆星中給這部電影1顆星，並說它「取得了《吸血新世紀》不溫不火的成就，卻勇於將其遺忘，把半生不死的留下來<ref>{{cite news |author=Roger Ebert |title=The Twilight Saga: New Moon |url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20091118/REVIEWS/911199998 |work=Rogerebert.com |publisher=The Chicago Sun-Times |date=2009-11-28 |accessdate=2009-11-25 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091122072733/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20091118%2FREVIEWS%2F911199998 |archivedate=2009-11-22 }}</ref>。」{{le|李察·羅珀|Mark Kermode}}以C−為《新月》評級，並將稱之為「單調乏味又極其慢的130分鐘的傳奇故事<ref>{{cite web |author=Richard Roeper |title=The Twilight Saga: New Moon Review |url=http://www.richardroeper.com/reviews/thetwilightsaganewmoon.aspx |publisher=RichardRoeper.com |accessdate=2009-11-25 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091127145123/http://www.richardroeper.com/reviews/thetwilightsaganewmoon.aspx |archivedate=2009-11-27 }}</ref>。」

